    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27576050_46_4075-4123",
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "range": "4075-4123",
      "markText": "中国传统政治既非君主专制，又非贵族政体，同时亦非阶级专政。中国传统政体，自当属于一种民主政体。”",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27576050&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=4075&rangeEnd=4123",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9d33212071a4c6f29d320c1?chapterUid=46&rangeStart=4075&rangeEnd=4123"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27576050_10_5059-5117",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "5059-5117",
      "markText": "钱穆的反问不无道理，我们能说现代社会的小学老师比一百年前钱穆小学时代的老师道德学问更高吗？如果不能，又是什么原因呢？",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27576050&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5059&rangeEnd=5117",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9d33212071a4c6f29d320c1?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=5059&rangeEnd=5117"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27576050_15_1185-1255",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "1185-1255",
      "markText": "于是改用“观法”，心中出现一种杂念，就反观自问，这种杂念从何而来。如此反问，则杂念不禁自止。如果杂念又生，就再反观自问，如此这般，一一息念。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27576050&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1185&rangeEnd=1255",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9d33212071a4c6f29d320c1?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1185&rangeEnd=1255"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27576050_52_3512-3570",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "3512-3570",
      "markText": "钱穆一再强调治学要破除门户，但他自己一味回护朱子，贬斥陆王，有些地方已经陷入他自己所竭力反对的门户意气之中而不自知。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27576050&chapterUid=52&rangeStart=3512&rangeEnd=3570",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9d33212071a4c6f29d320c1?chapterUid=52&rangeStart=3512&rangeEnd=3570"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27576050_48_4445-4511",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "4445-4511",
      "markText": "1973年，中大推出新的改革模式，新亚董事会完全丧失行政权力，原属之建筑物及不动产移交大学。至此，宋明书院到现代大学的转变终于完成。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27576050&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=4445&rangeEnd=4511",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9d33212071a4c6f29d320c1?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=4445&rangeEnd=4511"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27576050_46_3108-3154",
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "range": "3108-3154",
      "markText": "他们希望将近代西方意义的民主政治融入中国文化传统中去，肯定现代中国社会必当以民主政治为依归。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27576050&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=3108&rangeEnd=3154",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9d33212071a4c6f29d320c1?chapterUid=46&rangeStart=3108&rangeEnd=3154"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27576050_7_2777-2852",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2777-2852",
      "markText": "题目再考考钱穆。有客人说：“今晚由我来命题，就背诸葛亮骂死王朗吧。”但钱穆却扭扭捏捏，不再像昨天晚上那样主动、得意地表演了。客人们不知原因，不过也就不",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27576050&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2777&rangeEnd=2852",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9d33212071a4c6f29d320c1?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2777&rangeEnd=2852"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27576050_17_2741-2785",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "2741-2785",
      "markText": "所谓人微言轻，自古皆然。名报如《时事新报》，贤人如哲学家李石岑，都未能免俗，更何论其他？",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27576050&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2741&rangeEnd=2785",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9d33212071a4c6f29d320c1?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2741&rangeEnd=2785"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27576050_11_1871-1929",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1871-1929",
      "markText": "屠元博的父亲屠寄，字敬山，近代著名历史学家，尤精于蒙元史，著有《蒙兀儿史记》一书，书未成已名满中外。其时已退休居家。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27576050&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1871&rangeEnd=1929",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9d33212071a4c6f29d320c1?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1871&rangeEnd=1929"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27576050_28_1529-1622",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "1529-1622",
      "markText": "钱穆与胡适相遇于教师休息室，钱穆开口就说：“胡先生，《老子》年代晚，证据确凿，你不要再坚持了。”胡适则回敬道：“钱先生，你举的证据还不能使我心服；如果能使我心服，我连我的老子也不要了。”",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27576050&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1529&rangeEnd=1622",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9d33212071a4c6f29d320c1?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=1529&rangeEnd=1622"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27576050_11_6955-6971",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "6955-6971",
      "markText": "中学肄业是国学大师钱穆的最高学历",
